    "description": "<strong><i>Delve into harrowing dungeons, scour long-forgotten ruins from ancient realms, and battle legendary foes. The world of Renova beckons knightly heroes to come forth and vanquish its evil - the time is Nye!</i></strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Overview</strong></h2><br>Renova is a top-down ARPG that strives to bring a unique, innovative experience to players. Old-school in visual but refreshing in gameplay, Renova presents an action-driven combat, robust sandbox mode, and nostalgic fantasy adventure.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579200/extras/55f4d3fba3e6323c2364971de24b1fda.poster.avif?t=1672292401\" width=600 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579200/extras/55f4d3fba3e6323c2364971de24b1fda.webm?t=1672292401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579200/extras/55f4d3fba3e6323c2364971de24b1fda.mp4?t=1672292401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Game Features</strong></h2><br>Action-driven, real time combat in Renova means that players must be wary of how to time attacks and how to predict enemy moves. Distinguished from any run-of-the-mill hack and slash combat, Renova wants to challenge the players and provide them a fully-immersed experience.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579200/extras/ac2df00b3cc11eedd1829583058fe26d.avif?t=1672292401\" width=627 height=340 /></span><br><br>Through hand-crafted content and homely game design, Teutonic Games wishes our players a truly remarkable experience! <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1579200/extras/